tool_description.description:
Generates exercises for english lessons on the given topic. This is audio 
       exercise, that helps us to learn extracting information from text. In the  tag
       return one audio tag and list of objects wih 2 fields question and answer. Create exercise that way where
       questions and answers are different. 

               {{AUDIO}}

                   {{QUESTION}}
                   {{ANSWER}}



       - audio: string: max 500 token. Short exercise about given topic in 
       - question: string: a short question about an audio
       - answer: string: short answer on given question
